    <div class="help-card"><h3>Things to avoid</h3><ul><li>Trademarked IP (Stormwind, Jedi, Dark Brotherhood will be auto-flagged).</li><li>Profanity &mdash; most MMO name filters will reject and auto-rename you.</li><li>Names already used by famous raiding guilds (Method, Echo) unless roleplay tribute is intentional.</li><li>Overloaded punctuation and numbers &mdash; they look like throwaway alts.</li><li>Impossible-to-pronounce strings &mdash; raid leaders have to say it on voice chat.</li></ul></div>
